The paper deals with privacy-preserving analytics, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the storage and analysis of data, which is related to databases (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of algorithms to analyze data falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and the evaluation of the scheme's accuracy falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
